/// BETA Testing
This is the first of several maps that i am releasing in 
the next couple of weeks. This map is in BETA testing.
Please give me feedback on game play, fun and design
of the map for the final release and my future maps. 
Please leave feedback in comments here or by contacting
me via my email address.

/// Easter Egg / Secret Area
I am considering a secret area that leads from both
buildings and goes down into the bases foundations going
underneath the middle bridge and allowing the player to
shoot either side or go up into the enemy's base. I'd like 
to know if some people would like this in the final release?
